  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 2.7,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And you will write, you will speak.'",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No, no way.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "No way.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But the only thing-- he looked into the windows.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So when he walked in, so my brother's starting to say, 'What is the name of the household, and how many people?' And again and again, the same thing.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And then he wrote down.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And we moved into the next house.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We moved into the next house and did the same thing.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Then all of a sudden, the peasant that he was hiding us said, 'Look, there are strange people and there's some girls over there.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "You know, some girls are playing around there with the men, I mean.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "What are those girls-- those girls don't belong in that house.'",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So he said, 'Call your brother out.' So I'm not going to say, 'Brother, come out.' So I said it in a-- in a military way.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "He told me how to say [NON-ENGLISH], meaning, just 'Move out.'",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "He moved out.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And I said to my brother, I said, 'You know, Mr.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Kolacz is saying that those girls don't belong in this house.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But they identify them, try to do that.'",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "He walked over.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "He said, 'I want you to identify yourself.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Are you strangers in this town, are you village?' 'No, I'm from the same houses.'",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "The next Sunday-- so we scared them off.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We didn't take anything.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "As a matter of fact, at one of the last places that we went, the people were already appreciating that we're giving them so much courage that the war is towards the end-- and it was, so to say, towards the end-- that they gave us, they prepared already for Christmas the special cake, which is the--",
      "word_count": 57
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "--special cake made for Christmas.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "He said, 'You know what?",
      "word_count": 5
    }
  ],
